Common.LongDescription.Common.Text:
The property is positioned on the upper level of Warringah Mall’s Westfield (Next to HCF Dental/Eye Care) in the tightly held and highly sought-after Brookvale precinct. 

Westfield Warringah Mall is located 15 kilometres from the Sydney CBD in Sydney’s affluent Northern Beaches.

The centre is one of the largest shopping centres in the area, and well serviced by public transport with a dedicated bus interchange on its doorstep, the centre caters to a trade area population in excess of 298,000 residents (Source Westfield)


The property will be offered as a warm shell with contribution to fit-out for a brand-new open plan office/retail space customised to the future occupiers needs. 

•	Total area: 686sqm*-1,100sqm*
•	Good exposure
•	Central location 
•	High ceilings 
•	Blank canvass to customise fit out
•	Ample roof top parking at the front of the property
•	Ideal for a destination retail/fitness uses
•	Long lease term available

*approx
**Outlined indicative only

For further details, or to arrange an inspection please call exclusive leasing agents CBRE

Located on the corner of Pittwater Road & Cross Street, this superbly positioned retail space sits next to the newly opened Chemist Warehouse and metres to Westfield's Warringah Mall.

- 410sqm* ground floor retail + 80sqm* mezzanine
- 8 exclusive use car spaces
- 4m+ ceiling heigths
- 15m frontage
- Excellent signage opportunities including 40% share of two pylon signs
- Open plan, easy to configure retail space with minimal columns
- New ducted air conditioning throughout
- Male & female amenities, kitchenette and office on mezzanine
- Disabled access toilet on ground level

Would suit retail, showroom, medical, fitness and more (STCA).

For further details or to arrange an inspection, please call Amy Pfeiffer (CBRE) 0401 198 401 or Richard Rubenach (SHORE Commercial) 0412 267 440 / 02 9932 3405.

*Approx.

Common.LongDescription.Common.Text:
CBRE is pleased to offer a boutique development opportunity located in one of the Northern Beaches most prominent suburbs, Brookvale.

519 Pittwater Road, Brookvale benefits from the following key attributes:

- 518.4 sqm* site area
- Favourable B5 – Business Development zoning allowing for office premises, retail premises and shop top housing
- Maximum building height 11 meters
- Proximity to local amenities including Westfield Warringah Mall, existing and planned transport, schools and some of Sydney’s most iconic beaches
- Dual Frontage to Old Pittwater Road and Pittwater Road
- Current Improvements/NSA: 522sqm*
- An additional 106sqm* of outdoor terrace on the first floor

519 Pittwater Road, Brookvale is offered for sale via public auction on Tuesday, 1 August 2017 at 10.30am.
